reviewText: This is a very good dvd.  I really enjoy watching it.  I also have Vol. 1 My family always sing along while we watch.  I recommend this dvd and sll music from Luther Barnes & family.

This is another great product from the Barnes Family.  Props to big Mo for a great recording.  Several great songs like He keeps on blessing me!  I am not sure what happen between my line cut and the post house but it was a not that way when it left the truck but still very enjoyable concert!

I love listening to this family and Deborah Barnes, and her sisters has beautiful voices they sing like angels.  Luther is really a man after God's heart. I know that Rev. F. C Barnes is with the Lord singing for him now. You are all God sent!!
God Bless
